---
// Philosophy component - Product development philosophy
---

<section id="philosophy" class="py-24 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
	<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
		<!-- Section header -->
		<div class="text-center mb-16">
			<h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-6">
				Why Anotan?
			</h2>
			<p class="text-xl text-neutral-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
				Our product development philosophy is why we ship faster and build better.
			</p>
		</div>
		
		<!-- Philosophy grid -->
		<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
			<!-- Problem-First -->
			<div class="group">
				<div class="mb-6">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:bg-accent-200 transition-colors">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.172 16.172a4 4 0 015.656 0M9 12h6m-6-4h6m2 5.291A7.962 7.962 0 0112 15c-2.34 0-4.47-.881-6.08-2.33"></path>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">
						Problem-First
					</h3>
					<p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
						Ruthlessly focused on real, validated problems. Every product exists to solve something painful, urgent, or highly inefficient.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<!-- AI-First by Default -->
			<div class="group">
				<div class="mb-6">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:bg-accent-200 transition-colors">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"></path>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">
						AI-First by Default
					</h3>
					<p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
						We treat AI as a core creative partnerâ€”across strategy, design, and code. We leverage agents, copilots, and tools to accelerate and automate.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<!-- Lean & Iterative -->
			<div class="group">
				<div class="mb-6">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:bg-accent-200 transition-colors">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">
						Lean & Iterative
					</h3>
					<p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
						We ship fast, learn faster, and improve continuously. Always start with the smallest viable version.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<!-- Zero Waste -->
			<div class="group">
				<div class="mb-6">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:bg-accent-200 transition-colors">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 7l-.867 12.142A2 2 0 0116.138 21H7.862a2 2 0 01-1.995-1.858L5 7m5 4v6m4-6v6m1-10V4a1 1 0 00-1-1h-4a1 1 0 00-1 1v3M4 7h16"></path>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">
						Zero Waste
					</h3>
					<p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
						Every feature must make the product meaningfully faster, easier, or more magical. If it doesn't solve or scale, we cut it.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<!-- Data-Driven to an Extreme -->
			<div class="group">
				<div class="mb-6">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:bg-accent-200 transition-colors">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">
						Data-Driven to an Extreme
					</h3>
					<p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
						We use numbers to make every decision. If it's not validated by data, we question it hard and usually don't go for it.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<!-- Results -->
			<div class="group">
				<div class="mb-6">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:bg-accent-200 transition-colors">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">
						Proven Results
					</h3>
					<p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
						This philosophy has helped us ship 15+ ML pipelines, build tools used by 100+ operators, and consistently deliver 10x improvements.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		
		<!-- Bottom CTA -->
		<div class="mt-16 text-center">
			<p class="text-neutral-600 mb-6">
				Ready to see this philosophy in action?
			</p>
			<a 
				href="#contact" 
				class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-neutral-900 text-white font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-neutral-800 transition-colors duration-200"
			>
				Let's build something together
			</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</section> 